[Trello](http://www.trello.com) appears to be a terrific tool for project management.It makes collaboration easy and, collaborative and even entertaining.
The tool is super visual list, which makes interaction much easier.
Trello is not only limited to project management but I've been also using it as a way to organize everyithing. From personal 
projects and Columbia business school stuff to the things I need to take care before going into my summer internship. 
